h1. The Apache Karaf Team posted on January 30, 2015\\Karaf 3.0.3 released!

The Karaf team is pleased to announce the availability of [Karaf 3.0.3|index/community/download/karaf-3.0.3-release.html].

This is an update patch for Apache Karaf 3.0.x, containing many bug fixes, dependency updates, and improvements. New features highlights include: Spring 4.1.2.Release features, and provides ready to use jpa20 and jpa21 features.
For more information, please see the [release notes|index/community/download/karaf-3.0.3-release.html].
